reviews.title: Great food for a very friendly price.
reviews.text: We had a great lunch here with the grandchildren. The restaurant employs several people with a distance from the labour market who do their utmost to please the guests. The dishes on the menu are not very special, but very tasty. The service is very smooth and the prices are very friendly.
